 year timescale is available, it would allow one to explore the\nwave optics effect on microlensing light curve, if it occurs, or improve the\nPBH constraints in $M_{\\rm PBH}\\lower.5ex\\hbox{$\\; \\buildrel < \\over \\sim \\;$}\n10^{-11}M_\\odot$ even from a null detection.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 15 May 2019 10:05:25 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 10 Jun 2019 01:05:10 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 30 Mar 2020 15:32:54 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-03-31"}
