-the-art EDM models.\nThese results suggest that incorporating both item-skill relationships and\nforgetting effect improves over student models that consider one or the other.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 14 May 2019 16:41:03 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-05-17"}
